text: @atrupar @RepGrothman I switched to buying Vermont cheese, like Cracker Barrel instead of Sargento, after #Wisconsin became a tRump zone. Now, I’m even more happy I did! I see people coughing into cheese. After all, since Wisconsin doesn’t take #COVID19 seriously, why trust their food?
